cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.HC, cs.DB, cs.IR 

This paper discusses the ethical and legal issues related to data mining and consent, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses the data collection and mining landscape, which is related to databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper proposes best practices for data collectors, which is related to cybernetics (cs.CY).
